name: Space-Wars
body:
This is a small straty game that a group in ICS code club made and is very proud of.
They have worked hard to bring to you this little game.
    CONTROLS:
P1: 1,2,3 for lane select and q for suicide ship, w for shooter ship, and e for blocker ship
P2: 8,9,0 for lane select and i for suicide ship, o for shooter ship, and p for blocker ship

####HAVE FUN
